s for the construction industry produces and markets products for transport infrastructure and stores markets supplies and distributes jet fuel and aviation gasoline as well as provides refueling services to aviation companies the paz refining and logistics division manages refinery imports crude oil and related products manufactures oil distillates generates and sells electricity and offers logistic services including the storage and distribution of fuels as well as purchasing and supply services the company was formerly known as shell palestine and changed its name to paz oil company limited in  paz oil company limited was founded in  and is based in yakum israel detailed description holland buildingeuro parkkibbutzyakum  israelfounded in  employees phone     fax     key executives for paz oil company ltd mr yona fogel chief executive officer age  total annual compensation m mrs sharona novak chief financial officer and vice president age  total annual compensation m mr malachi alper vp ceo of refinery  logistics division and ceo of paz ashdod refinery ltd age  total annual compensation m mr amir erez chief executive officer of pazgas ltd age  total annual compensation m hagai zohar chief executive officer of paz lubricants  chemicals ltd and chief executive officer of pazkar ltd age  total annual compensation m compensation as of fiscal year  paz oil company ltd key developments paz oil company ltd to report q  results on may   may   paz oil company ltd announced that they will report q  results on may   paz oil company ltd q  earnings call may   may   paz oil company ltd q  earnings call may   paz oil company ltd to report fiscal year  results on mar   mar   paz oil company ltd announced that they will report fiscal year  results on mar   similar private companies by industry company name region alon israel oil company ltd middle eastafrica american israeli gas corporation ltd middle eastafrica baraka trading ltd middle eastafrica designer energy ltd middle east